{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f0472b745f","title":"向白军士兵抗口六条纲领的建议","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"94b12b6e30","index":0,"year":1934,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"f0472b745f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b0caa2a480","type":"paragraph","text":"向白军士兵抗口六条纲领的建议","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"8b93689225","type":"paragraph","text":"（1934年）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"4c24c778cc","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）要求北上抗日立即停止进攻苏区，实行中国人不打中国人，不打红军，枪口向日本帝国主义与汉好放！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"a9e8517550","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）要求士兵抗日的集会、结社、言论、行动自由，组织士兵抗日联合会，决定抗日大事与士兵本身的问题！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"55da006aca","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）改良士兵生活和待遇，要求发清欠的，反对打骂，反对法西斯蒂的压迫和居杀！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"4edb24317f","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）约定红军，双方互派代表，订立停战抗日同盟（五）杀死不准士兵抗日的官长变到真正抗日的红军中去！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"4a8f2ca555","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）不烧杀苏区工农，反对国民党压追民众抗日运动，联合全国同胞一致抗日！","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"43799983b9","type":"paragraph","text":"白军士兵弟兄们","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"1c97e485d1","type":"paragraph","text":"要想不做亡国奴，要救中国，就要立即团结起来实行这六条抗日纲领！红军时刻地准备着欢迎你们派代表前来共同订立停战抗日同盟，大家联合起来开到北方打日本去！","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"6c3bc54408","type":"paragraph","text":"白军十兵同红军联合起来！打倒日本帝国主义！打倒卖国贼国民党！","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"598cfa3bf0","type":"paragraph","text":"第五次反“围”失败，红一方面军被迫离开中央苏区，进行战略转移。图为江西于都红军桥，毛泽东就是从这里离开中央苏区，开始了二万五千里长征。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"77cfa3b4b7","type":"paragraph","text":"通道","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"69c89a964d","type":"paragraph","text":"湖东安","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"44c607234d","type":"paragraph","text":"湘江战役形势示意图1934.11.27--12.1","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"2b41e2aaf1","type":"paragraph","text":"新田","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"078cd0c9b9","type":"paragraph","text":"鑫景龙胜","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"0af379eef8","type":"paragraph","text":"南人","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"84569933c8","type":"paragraph","text":"宁远","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"8d6516e686","type":"paragraph","text":"嘉米桂林","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"558ae0a566","type":"paragraph","text":"蓝山西","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"1d5ef37fb6","type":"paragraph","text":"临武例","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"ca1ff3c960","type":"paragraph","text":"省松军调动及出路线","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"8af3b4d6f4","type":"paragraph","text":"2华城省","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"394702ec3e","type":"paragraph","text":"连县散军防墙线中央军消笔中央军","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"4d9977041a","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"c0504ff4a4","type":"paragraph","text":"修客川39338热楼","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"b8704fec27","type":"paragraph","text":"东省","index":26,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"ea06d9f6d4","type":"paragraph","text":"连山重菜战斗培点湘江战役形势示意图。","index":27,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"},{"id":"c5762ae7b0","type":"paragraph","text":"1934年12月18日，中共中央在贵州黎平召开政治会议，肯定了毛泽东改向国民党力量较弱的贵州前进的正确主张，使红军摆脱险境。图为黎平会议旧址。","index":28,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f"}],"page":{"id":"2f20e31d5b","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"f0472b745f","start":103,"end":105}}}},"__N_SSG":true}